# 🥗 Recipe Finder Project

A web app that helps users discover recipes based on ingredients and dietary preferences.  
It fetches live data from the **Edamam Recipe Search API**, allowing users to explore, filter, and save their favorite recipes.  

🚀 **Live Demo**  
- **Frontend:** [Netlify Deployment](https://st-recipefinder.netlify.app/)  
- **Backend:** [Coolify Deployment](https://ac80sgo8cw0wcswoscwsowck.hosting.codeyourfuture.io)  

---

## ✨ Features

✅ Search recipes by ingredient and diet type  
✅ View detailed recipe info (calories, servings, cuisine, etc.)  
✅ Filter recipes by calories and servings  
✅ Save and manage favorite recipes  
✅ Load more results with pagination  
✅ Responsive design for mobile and desktop  
✅ Full-stack setup: Netlify frontend + Coolify backend  

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- HTML, CSS, Typescript
- Netlify (hosting)

**Backend**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- CORS
- dotenv
- node-fetch
- Coolify (hosting)

**API**
- [Edamam Recipe Search API](https://developer.edamam.com/edamam-recipe-api)
